<li>May your memories bring you comfort during this sorrow.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy, we grieve with you.</li>
<li>Sending our love and prayers for peace and healing.</li>
<li>So very sorry for your loss.  May you find solace in your loved ones.</li>
